Now here you can you can add add the product from here also and you can enter the details from here shipping price, quantity price and the price of the product.

So it is up to the customer if he wants to accept the code or rejects the code.
The 500 quantity, 5000 quantity and 500 is the price.

We will approve the code and the quotation will be termed as an order and will be placed as an order.
So here the quotation is converted into an order.
Select the shipping, all the details, necessary information details and order is complete.
Now the order is complete and on the admin side you have received the order and you can check that the order is a custom order code here.
You can click on here and you can see this is the quotation.
